<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.2.1">
<l>pālaṉā yēḻula kuṇṭu pariviṉṟi</l>
<l>yālilai yaṉṉava cañceyyu maṇṇalār</l>
<l>tāḷiṇai mēlaṇi taṇṇan tuḻāyeṉṟē</l>
<l>mālumāl valviṉai yēṉmaṭa valliyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“The cool Tulsi [that is the] decoration on the foot-pair</l>
<l>of the eminent one who took a nap on a Banyan leaf,</l>
<l>faultless, having eaten the seven worlds, as an infant/guardian”,</l>
<l>thus is perturbed the foolish creeper[-girl] of me [who has done] bad deeds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
